{"tid":1849890,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"你寧願睇「良心渣片」定「黑心好片」?","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T06:23:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"615f231923afb24ceb09fd0a593ba9b2d0e36b2a","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"你寧願睇一套拍得有良心既渣片, 定係一套黑心既好片.<br />\n<br />\n今年賀歲檔有良心渣片《乜代宗師》(舒琪話套戲技巧差, 但冇偷雞, 好落力, 而且honest)<br />\n亦有黑心好片《肥龍過江》, 唔少行內人其實對套戲好評 (某位行內人網友話黃子華唔撚係黃, 捐款比星火好過睇《乜代宗師》, 但佢又話《肥龍過江》好睇. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;)<br />\n<br />\n結果, 票房證明觀眾寧願睇「良心渣片」多於「黑心好片」<br />\n《乜代宗師》成香港賀歲檔票房冠軍, <strong>反而《肥龍過江》竟然成為香港賀歲檔票房包尾</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n(反而, 《肥龍過江》係台灣, 馬來西亞同新加坡都票房大賣. &nbsp;但套片成本太高, 主要靠大陸票房定生死.) &nbsp;"},{"pid":"f14d32eb23ec7f7b9131ed618a2db3469eb0e8c9","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>舒琪: 《乜代宗師》</strong>&mdash;&mdash; <strong>都係嗰句：冇偷雞、好落力</strong>；唔算hilarious，但幾amusing；黃子華從來唔係一個出色嘅電影人（filmmaker），但卻<strong>具備咗一個電影人好重要嘅本質：honest</strong>，而且有嘢要講，仲係佢好相信嘅嘢。講得好唔好、技巧有幾高已經係另一個問題。我又相信（大部分）觀眾都收到佢嘅message。淨係呢樣，我已經覺得應該支持同肯定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>午夜翻牆: 看罷《肥龍過江》，跟老友兩眼對望，「好睇喎。」</strong>從事電影業界的他：「<strong>好睇，好似以前啲港產片</strong>。」《肥龍》由王晶監製，星皇朝出品，又有tvb參與（周麗淇主演），深黃要讚深藍，好像都要衝破心理關口。走到街上，二人談起戲中場面，及黃色電影圈，越談越興奮。我：「肯定是今年賀歲片質素第一。」他說：「好睇過《乜代宗師》。」想了一陣，他說：「<strong>其實近幾年沒有一齣賀歲片有此水平。</strong>」<br />\n....<br />\n<strong>殘忍的事實，是《肥龍》的喜劇work，電影娛樂性十足</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162719014225648&amp;set=a.10150175949200648&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10162719014225648%26set%3Da.10150175949200648%26type%3D3&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=fb61e00e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162719014225648&amp;set=a.10150175949200648&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/posts/548855269048054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frrroundmidnight%2Fposts%2F548855269048054&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=648336bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/posts/548855269048054</a>"},{"pid":"34818014b475052ae235c9daf3babea2acc16eb2","tid":1849890,"uid":27432,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"我寧願睇黑心好片<br />\n入去戲院訓好辛苦"},{"pid":"0a487eafee4e16441af04d16bb5158581c8573a5","tid":1849890,"uid":105511,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"肥龍過江係黑心渣片"},{"pid":"c7d3dcbbb9fe70b03fbc55d6f274988318e71a22","tid":1849890,"uid":195904,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"渣你老母閪 你鄉下方言？"},{"pid":"fd636e773c5bfd874752658b8146f1f77e07785f","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"順便講, 「良心渣片」&amp;「黑心好片」係以前某影評人傾計時提出. &nbsp;<br />\n佢舉例話《一路向西》係「良心渣片」, 《低俗喜劇》係「黑心好片」<br />\n<br />\n依家見彭浩翔投撚左共, 不得不服果位影評人既眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0975fcee2bc3063a6a1fdeb4c57a45ea6d548671","tid":1849890,"uid":132582,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"渣你老母片 爛片就爛片啦"},{"pid":"170675cc186a9dbb1f8e781cd059075a4d8179ae","tid":1849890,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03f73f2ed2ef2befdeda992cd839e13a83ea5a5","tid":1849890,"uid":45393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔幫"},{"pid":"3a0a8db692f478ab8df2f83844421a02fe674e19","tid":1849890,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c7d3dcbbb9fe70b03fbc55d6f274988318e71a22","tid":1849890,"uid":195904,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"渣你老母閪 你鄉下方言？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"渣字都唔識<br />\n乜咁渣架"},{"pid":"dcb82e1b0b6d9fcef463dc1e207f0a4eac940bd1","tid":1849890,"uid":159413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"唔撚睇"},{"pid":"62bc17a4c4a151820362a3fd8e6fede00ec08396","tid":1849890,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"睇老翻好片"},{"pid":"78c175fb690d04c643cae8f97175be1e0459b436","tid":1849890,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e89a76aad34e6c5c18a868057dba77cba5bfa4","tid":1849890,"uid":271413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔睇得唔得？"},{"pid":"8ed5832720a48681d70cf03f57ae50b5438d8077","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c7d3dcbbb9fe70b03fbc55d6f274988318e71a22","tid":1849890,"uid":195904,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"渣你老母閪 你鄉下方言？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"香港方言<br />\n<br />\n1998年香港影評都有用「渣片」呢個term<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.ph/PBHgd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FPBHgd&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=1b8858e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.ph/PBHgd</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《香港大夜總會》是一部渣片</strong>，這一點殆無疑義。至於是否好看或有趣？那就見仁見智，關鍵在於是否接受影片camp的一面。無論如何，影片趕在去年七月回歸之前跑來香港賁地拍攝，明顯與日本人看香港和九七的心理有直接關係。<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n作者: <br />\n李焯桃<br />\n刊物: <br />\n香港經濟日報<br />\nYear: <br />\n<strong>1998年</strong><br />\nMonth: <br />\n06月<br />\nDay: <br />\n20日"},{"pid":"666aeb59cc3dc5fab4b65769a727d282fda53f4c","tid":1849890,"uid":159183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"34818014b475052ae235c9daf3babea2acc16eb2","tid":1849890,"uid":27432,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"我寧願睇黑心好片<br />\n入去戲院訓好辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"2018年最差睇入場體驗<br />\n棟篤特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa72ec859dd80d94ccf17f8e5988754c5cf1c157","tid":1849890,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"認真答你,肥龍過江一撚定唔係好片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28496458509ccacd961be8d529884e087e99e2e","tid":1849890,"uid":261873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"未見過有黑心好片<br />\n<br />\n當年張藝謀拍英雄維穩<br />\n成堆明星<br />\n一樣好爛<br />\n都係要返去拍d低成本片先好睇<br />\n<br />\n彭浩翔投左共都係一樣<br />\n唔可能再拍得出好片"},{"pid":"690c4caa0bd952ac62c48b206c47469758fb158e","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b28496458509ccacd961be8d529884e087e99e2e","tid":1849890,"uid":261873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"未見過有黑心好片<br />\n<br />\n當年張藝謀拍英雄維穩<br />\n成堆明星<br />\n一樣好爛<br />\n都係要返去拍d低成本片先好睇<br />\n<br />\n彭浩翔投左共都係一樣<br />\n唔可能再拍得出好片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"個人覺得《英雄》正正就係係黑心好片<br />\n至少係商業角度上, 娛樂性十足<br />\n<br />\n(《英雄》係美國都票房勁收)"},{"pid":"a5bd57c330acb7c38a6696eb4882bbd53d3b54c9","tid":1849890,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"8ed5832720a48681d70cf03f57ae50b5438d8077","tid":1849890,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c7d3dcbbb9fe70b03fbc55d6f274988318e71a22","tid":1849890,"uid":195904,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"渣你老母閪 你鄉下方言？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"香港方言<br />\n<br />\n1998年香港影評都有用「渣片」呢個term<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.ph/PBHgd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FPBHgd&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=1b8858e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.ph/PBHgd</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《香港大夜總會》是一部渣片</strong>，這一點殆無疑義。至於是否好看或有趣？那就見仁見智，關鍵在於是否接受影片camp的一面。無論如何，影片趕在去年七月回歸之前跑來香港賁地拍攝，明顯與日本人看香港和九七的心理有直接關係。<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n作者: <br />\n李焯桃<br />\n刊物: <br />\n香港經濟日報<br />\nYear: <br />\n<strong>1998年</strong><br />\nMonth: <br />\n06月<br />\nDay: <br />\n20日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"真係無聽人講過 爛片就爛片 唔好搬啲文言文出黎"},{"pid":"2d7d082cdc63247a1ab79f63cfa34ff24a56dc56","tid":1849890,"uid":67407,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b28496458509ccacd961be8d529884e087e99e2e","tid":1849890,"uid":261873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"未見過有黑心好片<br />\n<br />\n當年張藝謀拍英雄維穩<br />\n成堆明星<br />\n一樣好爛<br />\n都係要返去拍d低成本片先好睇<br />\n<br />\n彭浩翔投左共都係一樣<br />\n唔可能再拍得出好片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"90年代賭神賭聖等賭系列由向華強勝兄弟出資出力又算唔算黑心好片？"},{"pid":"4f758c5794ded7580102980ed4c1d515792274cc","tid":1849890,"uid":313848,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"爛片就爛片，咩叫渣片<br />\n返去武漢啦，唔想搞大件事"},{"pid":"c66ac85c1e97385bb11f05185e783d24b2ceab30","tid":1849890,"uid":119145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"大陸爆撚晒肺炎 邊個得閒同你睇戲"},{"pid":"04a6e872502a83ac0397fa161bdd00e877e37057","tid":1849890,"uid":53209,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"依個po見到一堆不學無術 自以為是既連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f184e338e11f76916d90244d2cf7a65def78aede","tid":1849890,"uid":121865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"食一舊屎同兩舊屎的分別"},{"pid":"61ddb6d2d560f31c594d26f2508d07177dd2d20a","tid":1849890,"uid":312758,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4f758c5794ded7580102980ed4c1d515792274cc","tid":1849890,"uid":313848,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"爛片就爛片，咩叫渣片<br />\n返去武漢啦，唔想搞大件事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"爛片先係支語<br />\n<br />\n渣（第二音）片香港係8，90年代已經有人講緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975c14334699cf7f10c4f96979f2ecdda2872ca6","tid":1849890,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"黑心垃圾片拍得好我都唔會入場睇，最多等返幾個月上網睇高清藍光版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然你可以屌我唔尊重知識版權，不過你不仁我不義，我唔覺得有咩問題，況且我未見過屈服於極權之下嘅創作人有啲咩非常好嘅創作，好極都係爆谷級數，睇完最多消閑咗兩粒鐘，同外國嗰啲有靈魂有深度嘅商業電影完全冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍嗰個唔值得尊重，拍出嚟嘅戲又好極有限，咁我入場嚟做乜？"},{"pid":"1548075ad96e3c354b0e6f19cc84c9caaa315822","tid":1849890,"uid":228995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"《肥龍過江》睇預告我覺得唔太差<br />\n<br />\n之前《大師兄》都不過不失"},{"pid":"f266dc7c832c0c4f000911cbc5a34a0f08a74e5d","tid":1849890,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"975c14334699cf7f10c4f96979f2ecdda2872ca6","tid":1849890,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"黑心垃圾片拍得好我都唔會入場睇，最多等返幾個月上網睇高清藍光版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\"